---
title: Mexican Black Bean & Bacon Chilli & Avocado Salsa with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Say hello to the best bean in town, nutrient-packed black beans. They are wholesome and filling and go perfectly in a bowl with garlic rice and an avocado-cucumber salsa. Now cook it up in a fiery sauce to drive home those mouth-watering flavours

*We’ve replaced the soffrito mix in this recipe with onion due to local
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
